#### 2. **Unsafe Command Construction in KPM Wrapper (CRITICAL)**

**File**: `/src/kpm-integration/kpm-cli-wrapper.ts`
**Severity**: рҹ”ҙ **CRITICAL** (CVSS 9.9)
**CWE**: CWE-78 (OS Command Injection)

**Vulnerable Code**:
```typescript
// Line 54, 67, 80-89, 104, etc. - String interpolation in shell commands
private async executeCommand(args: string): Promise<string> {
  const cmd = `node "${this.kpmBinary}" ${args}`;  // Line 188 - UNSAFE
  const { stdout, stderr } = await execAsync(cmd, { timeout: 30000 });
}

// Caller examples:
await this.search(`query "${query}" --limit ${limit}`);  // Line 54
await this.install(`install "${packageName}" @${options.version}`);  // Line 82
```

**Attack Scenario**:
```
